Still nervously clanking his claws Scorponok tries to calm himself, "The
alliance?" he says. Then after he's reained his composure he screams.
"Scorponok, Terrorize" with that the scorpion changes to robot mode. He
puts his foot in the water then walks all the way in until he is sumberged
and starts following his radar towards london Island.
